  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb2\u0baf \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Temple bill broken and money stolen in Kandapalai",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A two-foot-tall silver billboard of the Tea Hill Sri Baladandayuthapani temple in the garden section of the Kandapalai police division was broken into by mysterious persons on Wednesday night and a large amount of money was stolen.",
        "The thieves broke through the window of the temple, broke the lock of the bill found inside the temple, stole a large amount of money found in the bill and threw the bill outside the temple.",
        "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the money found in the temple bill had not been taken by the temple administration for more than five years.",
        "With the help of a sniffer dog, the Kandhapalaya police are carrying out further investigations regarding the incident."
      ],
